plot: Supergirl and Nxyly battle for the Totem of Courage, and each get part of it. The part that Supergirl acquires causes chaos.

Nxyly tries to gain the first Totem, of Courage. It is split in two, causing raw courage to fill everyone in the vicinity. Sentinel, J'onn, Brainiac-5, and Dreamer are all affected, as are a scientist who discovers the courage to unleash her device which could destroy National City. Meanwhile, Supergirl and Nxyly both try to overcome tests of courage to gain control of the Totem.—Gislef
